==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Internationalist
<hw>In`ter*na"tion*al*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
is versed in the principles of international law.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A member of the International; one who believes in,
or advocates the doctrines of, the International.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>internationalistic</ent>⟦br⟧
